article_id:1718,category_name:公告,title_name:｢失落的龍絆官方推特帳號｣刊載【失落龍絆新手TIPS】公告,image_path:,message:<div>各位玩家您好</div><div><br></div><div>日前在「失落的龍絆官方推特帳號」上已公開適合剛加入遊戲的新手玩家參考的提示項目【失落龍絆新手TIPS】。</div><div>已統整【失落龍絆新手TIPS】的相關內容，並於本公告介紹。</div><div><br></div><hr><div>■長按篇</div><div>只要長按下方選單列的「主頁面」，就能移動到上次的任務！</div><div>想要建設或提升設施的等級時，只要長按下方選單列的「聖城」就能輕易移動！</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/447b989fee3f793650f347c056c57a2e.png"></div><div><br></div><div>■盧比獲得篇</div><div>裝備可在商店交換所「虛空之影討伐戰」內「特別」中交換的★5龍族「黃金法夫納」，並挑戰可獲得盧比的任務「通往黃金之道」，即可大量獲得盧比！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/27598cff96ed2f96e0a5d9449960e52f.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/34bae36c88ac458dcc04bba833c3c502.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■略過劇情篇</div><div>只要使用主線劇情的「劇情略過功能」，就能直接解放前10章，能夠立即參加活動！</div><div>玩家等級和設施等級也會相對提升！還能獲得強化素材等道具♪</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/a59971157d3b45d246a457272e86ac31.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■略過劇情篇2</div><div>使用「劇情略過功能」之後也能隨時回顧劇情。</div><div>也可以透過連載中的「那姆的驚險刺激冒險記！」以可愛的漫畫方式了解劇情內容喔♪</div><div><a href="https://comic.dragalialost.com/plotsynopsis/cht/#">https://comic.dragalialost.com/plotsynopsis/cht/#</a></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/3786c836460a539aa2375b5d60886bea.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■敵人攻擊篇</div><div>確認敵人的紅色攻擊標記並配合時機發動技能可以避免傷害。另外，滑動螢幕進行迴避動作時也能避免傷害。</div><div>進入紫色攻擊標記範圍時將無法迴避傷害，請特別留意！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/ac7b514fb0264e820f417597d3223fa8.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/6a42d12be791f91fdce362c44981f5ff.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■隊伍編制篇</div><div>編制隊伍時，只要裝備與角色同屬性的龍族和武器，就能發動「屬性一致加成」提升數值！</div><div>剛開始遊戲時較難湊齊相同屬性，先使用手邊現有的龍族和武器進行編制吧！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/e0f429b9098bc821d4d0204b1b772f04.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/ee8c0726d3279a544e37bae6a3fc5ed8.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■法夫納幣篇</div><div>收集法夫納幣，到商店交換所的「法夫納幣交換」交換稀有素材吧！</div><div>也可以交換「育龍庭園Ver.的龍族」，由於擁有不受屬性限制的能力，非常推薦新手使用♪</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/ed93a8040a12af90dc5a59b6a7be6a43.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/de0ee74a4f3d6662fe7041b3977ac82b.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■點擊素材篇</div><div>在武器生產＆強化以及建設頁面中點擊所需素材的圖示，即可確認可獲得該素材的任務！</div><div>若道具可於交換所獲得，將可直接進行交換！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/3e35d1cc1770128b95682a148eece71c.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/b689eb5a8950c2bf24fb8fccbbd0627e.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/07bbc9ae8bce15548d5f58fc15528eee.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/55686a23af812bbdb9b668c0aa8ee9cb.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■每日Mission篇</div><div>只要達成「每日Mission」即可獲得道具。</div><div>達成所有Mission還可獲得50個龍輝晶石！</div><div>別忘了每天進行挑戰喔！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/f4c01ee04428b8567cdfc3927104f3b4.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■王子育成演練篇</div><div>只要完成「王子育成演練」的作業，即可獲得強化素材和召喚券！</div><div>把完成所有作業當成目標吧♪</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/74b3a66d203101ada51e87881eb1fb82.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/c1dbf2b391ac74fe53db134605df1471.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■任務篇</div><div>即使任務失敗，也不會消耗能量和共鬥之翼。</div><div>歡迎玩家踴躍挑戰！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/aeb3f6b1c9955bdcccde0763f42cfc6a.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/b44ca8f7aa1021ef20093b08182525ce.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■龍輝護符篇</div><div>龍輝護符可透過任務、或是商店的「龍輝護符交換所」等方式獲得！</div><div>若不知該如何選擇時，推薦能夠提升技能傷害的護符，或是能夠發動連組加成的護符♪</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/51638f075280efee432b1dbada9d952e.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/e6d16db4fc2dbbcd6cdb845dc68cec09.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/ecab2e59705176faca0c8978cb6b71d6.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/2901ffc166a76e1f9dd6509cf059f493.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■商店篇</div><div>商店的「育成道具 育成組合包」中每天可免費進行1次「道具召喚」，還能使用盧比購買育成道具！</div><div>別忘了每天進行道具召喚喔！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/670371d66f475fe7b8075ec064ec6ed5.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/718b05c76f3250a9e2f5d04885d10f5e.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/1cc14d67c152ae46ddd2189cecafd8a0.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■交換所篇</div><div>商店中的交換所可以交換各式各樣的道具和設施！</div><div>其中包含了貴重的道具，請千萬不要錯過♪</div><div>設施是提升戰力時不可或缺的要素，記得要進行交換喔！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/313e3526fe893bb296319b50b070b84b.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/fa26d74e59d69680b8111b7f149962f8.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/2d9528501299e11d620bf6b1b7e3e018.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/014a2b65ecb89a057ffecb2ec0d3caf7.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div>■強化素材獲得篇</div><div>任務「通往成長之道」可獲得用來強化角色、龍族和武器的經驗值素材道具！</div><div>用來強化龍輝護符的道具則可以透過活動獲得！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/f43ff1ca5ceaab4ea2dcb7e49d6b5b09.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/feb0bb50c44b112441c099021d33c155.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■舊趣活動篇</div><div>參加可遊玩過去曾舉辦且常態性開放的部份設施活動「舊趣活動」，即可提升聖城的合計設施Lv！</div><div>參加的活動可隨時切換，歡迎玩家輕鬆挑戰♪</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/8894fdc6e6a67a4557f2a537b6ecad7b.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/6dfc28cff608f921449bee5977c08c53.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/1b511b4dd9a71017544a72eecbfb72f8.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/f0cb9ab396428a411785de1d95fbbe51.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■自動再戰功能篇</div><div>已完成所有任務Mission的任務，即可使用「自動再戰功能」自動反覆進行任務！</div><div>便於多次再戰收集素材♪</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/00f7ebac2622cda5524c779411e27cca.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/846d9ecfc70bd7aaeb29bcce6b4df2b8.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><hr><div>上述內容希望能夠讓新手玩家做為參考，並期待各位的踴躍挑戰。</div><div>也感謝一直支持遊戲的各位玩家在推特上對【失落龍絆新手TIPS】提供的眾多寶貴意見！</div><div><a href="https://twitter.com/dragalialost/status/1312649667570626567">期待能看見更多協助新手玩家的TIPS投稿！</a></div><div><br></div><div>今後也請您繼續支持【Dragalia Lost ～失落的龍絆～】</div><div>Dragalia Lost ～失落的龍絆～ 營運團隊　敬上</div>,start_time:1603260000,update_time1603259408